This repository contains the code for my driver testing blog series.

The test tool is inspired by the kdbus test suite [1] and the "driver" is
roughly inspired by this linuxvoice article [2].

Part 1: http://morbidrsa.blogspot.de/2015/03/testing-linux-drivers-part-i.html

[1] https://github.com/gregkh/kdbus/blob/master/test/kdbus-test.c
[2] http://www.linuxvoice.com/be-a-kernel-hacker/
